===Noun===
'''electrolyte'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[substance]] that, in [[solution]] or when [[molten]], [[ionize]]s and [[conduct]]s [[electricity]]
#{{physiology}} any of the various [[ion]]s (such as [[sodium]] or [[chloride]]) that [[regulate]] the [[electric charge]] on [[cell]]s and the [[flow]] of [[water]] across their [[membrane]]s
